{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"17215","heading":"National Marine Energy Centers","label":"17215 National Marine Energy Centers","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch152/schV/ptC","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsA prior section 17215, , , , related to authorization of appropriations, prior to the general amendment of this part by .Pub. L. 110–140, title VI, § 636121 Stat. 1688Pub. L. 116–260Dec. 19, 2007"],"amendments":["Prior ProvisionsA prior section 17215, , , , related to authorization of appropriations, prior to the general amendment of this part by .Pub. L. 110–140, title VI, § 636121 Stat. 1688Pub. L. 116–260Dec. 19, 2007"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the continuation and expansion of the research, development, demonstration, testing, and commercial application activities at the National Marine Energy Centers (referred to in this section as “Centers”) established as of ; andJanuary 1, 2020","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the establishment of new National Marine Energy Centers.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Location selection","label":"b Location selection","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Whether the institution hosts an existing marine energy research and development program.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Whether the institution has proven technical expertise to support marine energy research.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Whether the institution has access to marine resources.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Purposes","label":"c Purposes","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"advance research, development, demonstration, and commercial application of marine energy technologies in response to industry and commercial needs;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"marine energy systems of various technology readiness levels and scales;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a variety of technologies in multiple test berths at a single location;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"arrays of technology devices; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"interconnectivity to an electrical grid, including microgrids; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"collect and disseminate information on best practices in all areas relating to developing and managing marine energy resources and energy systems.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Coordination","label":"d Coordination","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To the extent practicable, the Centers shall coordinate their activities with the Secretary of Commerce, acting through the Undersecretary of Commerce for Oceans and Atmosphere, and other relevant Federal agencies.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Termination","label":"e Termination","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s17215","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs17215%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To the extent otherwise authorized by law, the Secretary may terminate funding for a Center described in paragraph (a) if such Center is under-performing.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
